ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR COMMUNITY SERVICE PROJECTS:

This software is developed with the intention of serving the community by 
reducing food waste and alleviating hunger. While the MIT License allows 
commercial use, we encourage users to:

1. Maintain the charitable and community service nature of this application
2. Consider contributing improvements back to the community
3. Use this software to benefit those in need rather than for purely commercial gain
4. Respect the privacy and dignity of all users, especially beneficiaries
5. Show gratitude and acknowledge Sri Nithish S (srinithishs004@gmail.com) for 
   his valuable contributions and inspiration in the development of this 
   humanitarian project

The authors and contributors of this project are committed to creating 
technology that serves humanity and builds stronger, more caring communities.

